    "detail": "This is my second time staying at Dorsett Regency Kuala Lumpur Hotel. Face some hiccups in booking as we are not aware that the connecting rooms are of different room types. However, Agoda and Dorsett Regency resolve the issues before our trip. Friendly and courteous staff. The staff are efficient in their service when we requested for extra towels, newspaper and tea spoons for the cakes we purchase at their Checkers Café. The rooms are cleaned up well and properly and the young housekeeper always make sure that we have bottled water and clean towels. The food street (carpark convert to make shift stalls at night), mama shop, coffee shop selling noodles and convenience stores are just available a stone throw away. Will re-visit Dorsett Regency again after they revamp the hotel this August.",
