    "detail": "First of all, the hotel room is very quiet, although you can literally see the jets landing or taking off every few minutes. Just close the window curtain, dim the light, and you'll feel like sleeping in sanctuary. This hotel is also more luxurious than most 5-star hotel in Kuala Lumpur, and the room is equipped with digital pad to control lighting, smart alarm, room service, etc. And you will be shocked with its affordable price. This hotel has a tunnel to KLIA Airport, with 24-hour free buggy car service. From the hotel lobby, it will take 5 minutes to reach your room, or 3 minutes to reach the airport (with buggy car). So, it is literally faster to reach the airport than to reach your room.",
