    "name": "Ceria Hotel Bukit Bintang",
    "detail": "I ADORE Ceria Hotel. Its my home when I am in Kuala Lumpur. I am reviewing it only because I dont forsee being in KL anytime soon and if I give it top reviews, the hotel will be overbooked. Its a FANTASTIC value for money hotel in the heart of Kuala Lumpur - behind one of the major shopping malls called Berjaya Times Square. The room is omg so lovely with its glass wall for the bathroom making your room look huge. The windows are from ceiling to floor, the tv channels include the movie channel, the staff is omg friendly AND sincere, the manager is dam hot hot hot and SEXY. Now that the cat is out of the bag, I just pray that they wont skyrocket the rates. If you are a sucker for overpriced glitz with no soul, look somewhere else. If you appreciate FAST wifi connections, a helpful staff, a hot and sexy hotel manager you could look at every day and dam gud value for money, think CERIA HOTEL where NHM stays when she is in KL. ",
